post_content: A sweet-sounding, great-feeling dreadnought that has plenty of mojo and won’t break the bank, it features a laminated basswood top, back and sides, with a dark-stained maple fingerboard and bridge. Other great features include quartersawn "X"-bracing, black neck and body binding, comfortable "C"-shaped neck profile, 20 frets, single-ply black pickguard and chrome tuners. ";"9200
